        dd <ruby>假<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㆤˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>好<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄜˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>心<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㆬ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>亦<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄚㆷ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>假<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㆤˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>歹<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄞˋ/ㄆㆮˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>心<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㆬ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>半<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄨㆩ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>呵<rt>&thinsp;ㄜ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>咾<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㄜˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>半<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄨㆩ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>壓<rt>&thinsp;ㄚㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>制<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>叫<rt>&thinsp;ㄍ丨ㄜ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>伊<rt>&thinsp;丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>回<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㆤˊ/ㄏㆤˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>會<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㆤ˫/ㄏㄨㆤ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>失<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㆵ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>禮<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㆤˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。
        dd
